T1  - Tough love for lazy kids: Dynamic insurance and equal bequests
AU  - Slavík, Ctirad
AU  - Wiseman, Kevin
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 27
SP  - 64
EP  - 80
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/01/01/
